name: Tcpip hl7 engine
tagline: Hl7 engine written in c# by: Stephen Wilson
body:
### Welcome to Neural Network TechNologies TCP/IP C# Interface engine
This is an open source interface engine written by Stephen Wilson for the purpose of eventually selling it along with other products from NNTN Inc.


### Authors and Contributors
In 2014, Stephen Wilson (@stephen6465)founded Neural Network TechNologies in order to achieve one goal: Make programs work smarter and conquer the world using software.

### Support or Contact
If you end up being fortunate enough to use this software than please let me know and let me know if you have any questions or need help in your project as I work for peanuts... lol (@stephen6465)
